[30;1m46 | [0m[35mthis Bandit processes each file, builds an AST from it, and runs appropriate[0m
[30;1m47 | [0m[35mplugins against the AST nodes. Once Bandit has finished scanning all the files[0m
[30;1m48 | [0m[35mit generates a report.[0m

[30;1m122 | [0m[35ma change being requested during the review cycle), please perform a git squash[0m
[30;1m123 | [0m[35monce a reviewer has approved your pull request.[0m

[30;1m125 | [0m[35mA squash can be performed as follows. Let's say you have the following commits:[0m
